The system should integrate with just about every bloody device a user can get their hands on:


* Pretty, modern webui
* Downlevel webui for older browsers
* Easy email interaction
    * Incoming
        * create or update a task
    * Outgoing
        * reminders
        * subscribe to tasks

* PDA browser interaction
* Incoming voicemail gateway "Leave a message, create a task"

* Outoging voice gateway. "Call me with a reminder"

* ICal feed of due dates
* RSS feed of updates

* Web Services API so users can surprise us
